---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Projects
description: Side projects, a startup, and experiments by Ziyan Song.
bodyClass: projects-page
---
<section class="wrap page-intro">
  <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>
  <h1 class="page__title">Things I've built.</h1>
  <p class="page__lede">
    A mix of side projects, a startup, and experiments, mostly across iOS, systems, and
    the serverless glue in between. Each one taught me something I couldn't have learned
    from a tutorial.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="wrap">
  <div class="bento">
    {% for p in collections.projects %}
      <a class="bento-card bento-card--{{ p.data.size or 'wide' }} {% if p.data.accent %}bento-card--accent{% endif %} {% if p.data.preview %}bento-card--has-media{% endif %}" href="{{ p.url }}">
        {% if p.data.preview %}<div class="bento-card__media"><img src="{{ p.data.preview }}" alt="" loading="lazy" /></div>{% endif %}
        <div class="bento-card__top">
          <span class="bento-card__cat">{{ p.data.category }}</span>
          <span class="bento-card__year">{{ p.data.year }}</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="bento-card__title">{{ p.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="bento-card__blurb">{{ p.data.summary }}</p>
        {% if p.data.tags %}
          <ul class="taglist">
            {% for t in p.data.tags %}<li>{{ t }}</li>{% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="bento-card__more">View project →</span>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
